She finished her drink and stood up. "Yes, let's see what our work 
has turned up."  She started to walk out of the mess hall. "I just 
hope this plan of mine works. Or else, well, the Matrix help us if it 
doesn't. I don't want to lose any more of our troops.  I don't want 
to risk any more of our teams lives if it can be helped.  I don't 
mind getting killed to help out our team, but I don't want to put the 
rest of the team in jeopardy if it can be helped."  She walked down 
the hall, thinking about how she would have to rig up the controls 
for the clone.
